<!-- WHAT IS AMIKECO -->

<div class="what-is-amikeco-container">
  <div class="what-is-amikeco-headline">
    <div class="title-flat">
      <%= image_tag "bridge_flat.png", style: "width: 90px; height: 90px;", id: "bridge-flat" %>
    </div>
    <h1><strong>Connecting people from different generations</strong></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="what-is-amikeco-subheadline">
    <h3>What is amikeco?</h3>
  </div>

  <div class="what-is-amikeco-content">

    <div class="what-is-amikeco-card">
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-avatar">
        <%= image_tag "avatar_elderly.png", class: "card_amikeco_avatar" %>
      </div>
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-card-head">
        <h3>Enjoyment</h3>
      </div>
      <p>After retirement many seniors lose connection to close people around them. A big amount of them live alone and would <strong>enjoy company</strong> outside of their regular routine.<br> Someone who they could let partake in their <strong>life experience, and share stories </strong>with.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="what-is-amikeco-card">
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-avatar">
        <%= image_tag "avatar_bridge.png", class: "card_amikeco_avatar" %>
      </div>
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-card-head">
        <h3>Commonality</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-card-body">
        <p>Amikeco is a service that connects people from the community with <strong>shared interests</strong> whose paths might never have crossed. <br> The goal is to bring a little bit <strong>more positive energy</strong> in the lives of younger and older people and with time maybe even curtail the generation gap.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="what-is-amikeco-card">
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-avatar">
        <%= image_tag "avatar_young.png", class: "card_amikeco_avatar"%>
      </div>
      <div class="what-is-amikeco-card-head">
        <h3>Experience</h3>
      </div>
      <p>On the other hand younger people can gain a lot out of spending time with a senior. <strong>A different perspective on life and serious advise </strong>from people who have tried and achieved so many things before. And not to forget will they cheer and freshen up this person's life.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="second-arrow-down" class="arrow-down">
    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  </div>
</div>
